Dubious dealings 

Booking.com couldn’t do anything because the communication and transaction happened outside the app. 

After investigations, they found out that the culprit was a man using a woman’s pictures on Instagram. Wambui decided not to pursue the matter further. The host, however, removed the property from the site and took down the Instagram account. 



